    "description": {
      "zh": "NightForce NXS 2.5-10x24毫米瞄准镜在较为紧凑的尺寸下提供了从2.5倍到10倍的变焦倍率。这种瞄准镜被设计用于狩猎及实战射击，能够承受强大的后坐力，并且在无论远近的距离上都能提供精准的射击。得益于极佳的可靠性，它能够安装于任何口径的武器上。该瞄准镜在全世界多个国家的民用及军用领域均获得了广泛认可。 ",
      "en": "The Nightforce NXS 2.5-10x24mm scope combines compact size with a wide magnification range from 2.5x to 10x. Designed for hunting and practical shooting, it is capable of withstanding powerful recoil and placing effective fire on short to long ranges. It has gained wide recognition among both civilian shooters and military operators of many countries worldwide."
    },
